各方面多数认定朝鲜实施了第四次核试验确为事实，但氢弹的次级没有被引爆<ref>{{cite news|title=First on CNN: North Korea may have tested components of a hydrogen bomb|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2016/01/28/politics/north-korea-hydrogen-bomb-test/index.html|agency=CNN|date=2016-01-29|accessdate=2016-01-29|archive-date=2016-01-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160129160607/http://edition.cnn.com/2016/01/28/politics/north-korea-hydrogen-bomb-test/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，或者此次试验是被称为“助爆型”的增强型原子弹爆炸试验，而非朝鲜所称的氢弹<ref>{{cite news|title=CISAC Nuclear Expert Analyzes North Korean Hydrogen Bomb Claims|url=https://cisac.fsi.stanford.edu/news/cisac-nuclear-expert-analyzes-north-korean-hydrogen-bomb-claims|date=2016-01-07|agency=Freeman Spogli Institute for International Studies|accessdate=2016-01-20|archive-date=2016-01-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160111082313/http://cisac.fsi.stanford.edu/news/cisac-nuclear-expert-analyzes-north-korean-hydrogen-bomb-claims|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=热点：多数认为朝鲜核试为助爆型 专家警告不容疏忽|url=http://china.kyodonews.jp/news/2016/01/112465.html|website=共同网|date=2016-01-09|accessdate=2016-01-20|archive-date=2016-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160109135626/http://china.kyodonews.jp/news/2016/01/112465.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=朝鲜试爆氢弹说法遭质疑 外媒:专家称技术达不到|url=http://www.cankaoxiaoxi.com/world/20160107/1047211.shtml|accessdate=2016-01-07|agency=参考消息|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160113170507/http://www.cankaoxiaoxi.com/world/20160107/1047211.shtml|archivedate=2016-01-13}}</ref>，即便如此作为助爆剂的聚变材料核聚变反应是否被触发仍是疑问（事后韩国核能安全所在空气采样中检测出了可能来自[[核裂变|核裂变]]反应的[[氙|氙]]，但没有提及检出[[核聚变|核聚变]]的特征产物[[氦|氦]]<ref>{{cite news|title=韩国称检测到少量氙气|url=http://v.ifeng.com/news/world/201601/01f576c7-62ae-469a-9e29-da2a745e5b08.shtml|agency=CCTV|date=2016-01-08|accessdate=2016-01-29|archive-date=2016-02-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160205011745/http://v.ifeng.com/news/world/201601/01f576c7-62ae-469a-9e29-da2a745e5b08.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>）<ref>{{cite news|title=朝鲜的“氢弹”试验到底成功没？|url=http://www.ftchinese.com/story/001065634|agency=FT中文网|accessdate=2016-01-20|archive-date=2016-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160109212714/http://www.ftchinese.com/story/001065634|dead-url=no}}</ref>。专家分析认为朝鲜核武器开发取得切实进展，可谓是向着氢弹又迈进了一步，并给出了不应疏忽的警告<ref>{{cite web|author=Jeffrey Lewis|title=OPINION: Has North Korea really tested a hydrogen bomb?|url=http://english.kyodonews.jp/news/2016/01/392013.html|website=共同网|date=2016-01-09|accessdate=2016-01-20|archive-date=2016-01-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160112175753/http://english.kyodonews.jp/news/2016/01/392013.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

